{"tid":2478042,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬體會隻Lemar其實點解咁多機會？","createTime":"2021-04-06T18:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T21:18:55.000Z","uid":68916,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"12863300ab2c2ec7079743df3d5d86002050d011","tid":2478042,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"少睇佢，不過睇親都廢，等真球迷入嚟解下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世盃前一季，法甲2g 8a都入選到23人，雖然話就話Coman傷，但佢都唔係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就執到個世盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後去馬體，三季踢咗都20+場，共入四球<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該好難可以兜到係勁<br />\n但係都照用唔清，仲要近排法國都仲有揀佢，差唔多踢足咁多分鐘，逼到Coman同Odem打後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講來講去真係勁都只係得16 17聯賽冠軍嗰年"},{"pid":"4eb73bfb23d07364656fc4aa6f8951b97f0c07ad","tid":2478042,"uid":59818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"雲加當年差啲用92m買咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1188ea71bc61e6e0dda481213e7437bf478432e","tid":2478042,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"不過講真 馬體套戰術 咩翼鋒都死"},{"pid":"a1d42e54161af17e1b08e09ed1d78acf265abf3f","tid":2478042,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"講緊omlo ？"},{"pid":"e107372a378f592b76f27ef8fb102f6297191316","tid":2478042,"uid":133756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"咁貴買完唔用<br />\n想俾老細屌咩"},{"pid":"789410bec6394aa7e217cbe4c30f572ae129c5e6","tid":2478042,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e107372a378f592b76f27ef8fb102f6297191316","tid":2478042,"uid":133756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi